


https://godoc.org/golang.org/x/tools/godoc/vfs#FileSystem
type FileSystem
type FileSystem interface {
    Opener
    Lstat(path string) (os.FileInfo, error)
    Stat(path string) (os.FileInfo, error)
    ReadDir(path string) ([]os.FileInfo, error)
    RootType(path string) RootType
    String() string
}
The FileSystem interface specifies the methods godoc is using to access the file system for which it serves documentation.



Make a corpus using FileSystem:
func NewCorpus(fs vfs.FileSystem) *Corpus

